Description: 
   Description: 
    Provides tools to generate synthetic electronic health record datasets, including patients, encounters, vitals, laboratory tests, medications,
    procedures, and allergies. Optional modules support COVID-19â€“focused profiles and computed tomography (CT) research views. Generated datasets can be 
    exported to comma-separated values (CSV), SQLite databases, and Excel workbooks for use by researchers and developers.
